            <title>联想 Yoga Slim 7x 笔记本亮相：可选骁龙 X2 Plus / Elite 芯片，下半年上市</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/911/321.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/911/321.htm</guid>
